extraction.query:
SELECT *
FROM
  SERVPROV S,
  LOCATION L,
  LOCATION_REFNUM LR
WHERE
  S.SERVPROV_GID = L.LOCATION_GID
  AND L.LOCATION_GID = LR.LOCATION_GID
ORDER BY
  L.LOCATION_NAME
